						"created":"2024-02-20T02:14:12.600305+01:00",
						"description":"AR3DMat Powder Coated Aluminum Frames\" is a versatile material asset designed for Blenderkit, created procedurally within Blender. This material offers a range of customizable features, including adjustable hue/color, roughness, metalness, rust level, and rust scale. With its procedural nature, this asset provides flexibility and control, allowing users to achieve various looks and textures for their aluminum frame designs. Whether you're aiming for a sleek, modern finish or a weathered, rustic appearance, \"AR3DMat Powder Coated Aluminum Frames\" offers the tools to achieve your desired result.",
